I meant to leave that stuff at your apartment. 我本来想把那些东西留在你家里的。
I meant to tell you, I don't love you anymore. 我本来想告诉你，我不再爱你了。
You mean to tell me you can't find a room? 你是想告诉我，你找不到房间了？
You didn't pay back the money you owe me. 你欠我的钱还没还呢。
I meant to give it to you this morning. 我本来想今天早上给你的。